Author: Daniel Carpenter [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Daniel Carpenter <daniel.carpenter@chickasaw.net>
Description: This package implements CMAC branding in ggplot2. This package 
    includes the base gray and blue gradients, text colors, and the data 
    visualization colors. The package works natively with ggplot2 for ease 
    of brand implementation.
